                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020918-76-off407 t18020918-76-cd408"></join>, a painting and frame, value 10s. 6d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18020918-76-victim579" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Atkinson
                  <interp inst="t18020918-76-victim579" type="surname" value="Atkinson"></interp>
