                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020918-76-defend577 t18020918-76-punish412"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
